  "time_ut": 1661154829,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a \u0d85\u0db4\u0dd4\u2018\u0dbb \u0d85\u0da7\u0d9a\u0da7 8,80,000\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0da9",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "8,80,000 fined for selling rice at high price",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Anuradhapura Additional Magistrate Mrs. Rudrika De Silva Hewawasam and Kahatagasdigilia Magistrate Mr. Wimal Weerasinghe ordered eight shopkeepers who were found guilty before the court for selling rice at a price higher than the government control price to pay a fine of eight lakh and eighty thousand rupees.",
        "According to this, among the eight suspected shop owners, five people were separately fined one lakh rupees each, one shop owner was fined one lakh thirty thousand rupees and another shop owner was ordered to pay a fine of eight lakh eighty thousand rupees.",
        "Anuradhapura New Puttalam Road Second Step Mananadu Grocery and Farm Shop Manager M. Wickramapala, Manager of Jayanthi Mawatha Hemamali Traders, Anuradhapura DG Vijitha, Manager of Laksara Stores, Anuradhapura Airport Road S Sugathapala, Manager of Induwara Stores opposite Saliyapura Railway Station G. W. P. P. J Jayasena, manager of Parasangaswewa Ratmale Junction Raja Stores, SE Lalana Charinda Kumara, manager of Anuradhapura Tihiyagama Junction Food Market, P Upali Piyaratne, manager of Kapuwatta Rasidu Super, Yakalla Megodawewa, and Sadas Mohammad Siras, manager of Testco Lanka Rice Mills, Shravastipura.",
        "Chief Senior Investigation Officer of the Anuradhapura District Office of the Consumer Affairs Authority B. A5. C. P. Mr. Perera and the investigating officer Mr. Saman Abeysinghe produced the suspected shopkeepers before the Anuradhapura Additional Magistrate Court and the Kahatagasdigilia Magistrate Court."
      ],
